==Drinking (if the player has not drunk the [[bottle of soul]])==
* {{tbox|You take a second look at the expiry date on this drink. It looks like it will be extremely potent and dangerous. Are you REALLY sure you want to drink this?}}
* {{tselect|Are you REALLY sure you want to drink this?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** {{mes|You drink the bottle of soul juice.}}
** {{tbox|Something taps you on the shoulder. You feel the presence of Death.}}
** '''Death:''' What do you think you are doing?
** '''Player:''' Death? I'm just charting the sea!
** '''Death:''' How does that involve desecrating souls?
** '''Player:''' I was just enjoying a drink!
** '''Death:''' That was a trapped soul, you fool.
** '''Player:''' I thought it was just some sort of marketing nonsense!
** '''Death:''' Well it wasn't. Hold still whilst I extract your unfortunate victim.
** {{tbox|You feel a painful shiver in your spine.}}
** '''Death:''' It is done. Do not be so careless again, or I shall not be so forgiving.
** '''Player:''' I'm so sorry!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** {{tact|end}}

==Drinking (if the player has already drunk the [[bottle of soul]])==
* {{tbox|You take a second look at the expiry date on this drink. It looks like it will be extremely potent and dangerous. Are you REALLY sure you want to drink this?}}
* {{tselect|Are you REALLY sure you want to drink this?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** {{tact|Player does [[Vengeance]] animation and takes 90% of their maximum hitpoints in damage.}}
** {{tbox|Something grips you hard on the shoulder. You shiver in agony.}}
** '''Death:''' Did you forget our last little chat?.
** '''Player:''' Not at all! This isn't another real soul is it?
** {{tbox|You feel death nod inside your head.}}
** '''Death:''' Let me extract this poor soul.
** {{tbox|You feel a painful shiver in your spine.}}
** '''Death:''' It is done. Consider this pain next time you uncork any bottle. Do not let me have to talk to you a third time.
** '''Player:''' I'll be more careful, I promise!
** '''Death:''' Hmph.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** {{tact|end}}
